---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contacto VIP | LUXO DR Luxury Rentals">
<!-- Top Navigation -->

<main class="pt-20">
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-black/60 z-10"></div>
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Luxury black sports car parked on a tropical coastline" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDO0bvaH8tj56oYhK6Z5bfX31j9gLKcmilfq5vGxgVMewxpuWTFByR2FX1v3t8a4XeUptjgyHMNhzv99PObL252s9O0Otqey1B7ncaEq2DSZ1FhgF6oReg2gSfoty07M67iazoVhxE8LLGMwrkd_Wq3uiIUOLkrujTQ25UrPQZV_uvA0S8x2IgAkSUexfmjOXxbl0amANOh-n509ueKHwTf-CPDFEB2Ti1_GkjZOPr1KbjF0seWyq4Em16RRCECkdd7Mg4oVUrKJBDp"/>
</div>
<div class="relative z-20 text-center px-6 max-w-4xl">
<span class="text-primary font-bold tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-xs mb-4 block">Atención Personalizada 24/7</span>
<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-none uppercase">
                    Contacto <span class="text-primary">Exclusivo</span>
</h1>
<p class="text-slate-300 text-lg md:text-xl font-light max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                    Nuestro servicio de Concierge VIP está disponible para coordinar su experiencia de conducción de lujo en la República Dominicana.
                </p>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Contact Section -->
<section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-24 grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20">
<!-- Form Side -->
<div>
<div class="mb-12">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 uppercase tracking-tight">Solicitud de Consultoría</h2>
<div class="h-1 w-20 bg-primary mb-6"></div>
<p class="text-slate-400 font-light">Complete el siguiente formulario y un Concierge asignado le contactará en menos de 15 minutos.</p>
</div>
<form class="space-y-8">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
<div class="group">
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary mb-2">Nombre Completo</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-white/20 focus:ring-0 focus:border-primary text-white py-3 px-0 transition-all placeholder:text-white/20" placeholder="Ej. Alejandro Jensen" type="text"/>
</div>
<div class="group">
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary mb-2">Correo Electrónico</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-white/20 focus:ring-0 focus:border-primary text-white py-3 px-0 transition-all placeholder:text-white/20" placeholder="email@dominio.com" type="email"/>
</div>
</div>
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
<div class="group">
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary mb-2">WhatsApp / Teléfono</label>
<input class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-white/20 focus:ring-0 focus:border-primary text-white py-3 px-0 transition-all placeholder:text-white/20" placeholder="+1 809-000-0000" type="tel"/>
</div>
<div class="group">
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary mb-2">Vehículo de Interés</label>
<select class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-white/20 focus:ring-0 focus:border-primary text-white py-3 px-0 transition-all appearance-none cursor-pointer">
<option class="bg-background-dark">Lamborghini Urus</option>
<option class="bg-background-dark">Rolls-Royce Cullinan</option>
<option class="bg-background-dark">Ferrari F8 Tributo</option>
<option class="bg-background-dark">Mercedes G-Wagon AMG</option>
</select>
</div>
</div>
<div class="group">
<label class="block text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-primary mb-2">Mensaje o Requerimiento Especial</label>
<textarea class="w-full bg-transparent border-0 border-b border-white/20 focus:ring-0 focus:border-primary text-white py-3 px-0 transition-all placeholder:text-white/20 resize-none" placeholder="Describa sus necesidades especiales para su estancia..." rows="4"></textarea>
</div>
<button class="w-full bg-primary hover:bg-white text-background-dark py-5 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.3em] transition-all flex items-center justify-center gap-3" type="submit">
                        Enviar Solicitud VIP
                        <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-xl">arrow_right_alt</span>
</button>
</form>
</div>
<!-- Details Side -->
<div class="flex flex-col gap-12">
<!-- Direct WhatsApp CTA -->
<div class="bg-primary/5 border border-primary/20 p-8 rounded-lg relative overflow-hidden group">
<div class="absolute -right-8 -bottom-8 opacity-10 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-9xl">chat</span>
</div>
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-2 uppercase tracking-tight">Atención Inmediata</h3>
<p class="text-slate-400 mb-6 font-light">¿Necesita asistencia ahora mismo? Hable directamente con un Concierge vía WhatsApp.</p>
<a class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-primary text-background-dark px-8 py-3 font-bold uppercase text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-colors" href="#">
                        Consultoría vía WhatsApp
                    </a>
</div>
<!-- Locations Grid -->
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
<div class="border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-6">
<h4 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary mb-3">Punta Cana Desk</h4>
<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
                            Marina Cap Cana, Edificio Premium, Suite 402.<br/>
                            Punta Cana, Rep. Dom.
                        </p>
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-widest">+1 809 555 0199</p>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">pc@luxo-dr.com</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="border-l-2 border-primary/30 pl-6">
<h4 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-primary mb-3">Santo Domingo HQ</h4>
<p class="text-slate-300 text-sm font-light leading-relaxed mb-4">
                            Av. Winston Churchill, Torre Empresarial, Nivel 12.<br/>
                            Santo Domingo, Rep. Dom.
                        </p>
<div class="space-y-1">
<p class="text-xs font-bold text-white tracking-widest">+1 829 555 0100</p>
<p class="text-xs text-slate-500">sdq@luxo-dr.com</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Map Section -->
<div class="flex-grow rounded-lg overflow-hidden border border-white/5 relative min-h-[300px]">
<div class="absolute inset-0 map-placeholder bg-background-dark flex items-center justify-center">
<img class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover opacity-40 grayscale contrast-125" data-alt="Abstract dark map of Caribbean islands with gold markers" data-location="Dominican Republic" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCvSmEkMfv_QjBqkA_BlQzH67htQkYI8DmqWxZCGEPVZ-sUgIqUvei2YO3wt9XK1uaJAKWJ9ldM-x-y5VkaxMnjYbFG_FNVpXjqQsruU_fhn0jKHKPRI5b-j0Ug9rFb0VVFbYO1Syc7S4sEiMsvkmo_Hx5x1XH4zh6FDa4MqBaz2sIuw08BeuKBF1qwrg8spi75fV8n4w4fT7LnyTRJ_64e3G7KZ3nN_mbPpwtU1bwXuPY23H3whwbrWMkR0_r_bSphZ0lyqdYt25tE"/>
<!-- Marker Punta Cana -->
<div class="absolute top-[40%] right-[20%] group">
<div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="absolute w-8 h-8 bg-primary/20 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">location_on</span>
<div class="absolute bottom-full mb-2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity bg-background-dark border border-primary/50 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary uppercase whitespace-nowrap">Punta Cana</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Marker Santo Domingo -->
<div class="absolute top-[50%] left-[40%] group">
<div class="relative flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="absolute w-8 h-8 bg-primary/20 rounded-full animate-ping"></div>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl">location_on</span>
<div class="absolute bottom-full mb-2 opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity bg-background-dark border border-primary/50 px-3 py-1 text-[10px] font-bold text-primary uppercase whitespace-nowrap">Santo Domingo</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="absolute bottom-4 left-4 right-4 bg-background-dark/80 backdrop-blur p-4 border border-white/5">
<p class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 font-bold uppercase tracking-widest">Localizaciones Disponibles</p>
<p class="text-xs text-white">Servicio de entrega VIP en todos los aeropuertos internacionales.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Experience Banner -->
<section class="bg-primary py-16">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-8">
<div>
<h3 class="text-background-dark text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight mb-2">Lujo sin compromisos.</h3>
<p class="text-background-dark/80 font-medium">Únase al círculo exclusivo de conductores Luxo DR.</p>
</div>
<button class="bg-background-dark text-primary px-10 py-4 font-black uppercase tracking-widest text-sm hover:scale-105 transition-transform">
                    Ver Catálogo 2024
                </button>
</div>
</section>
</main>
<!-- Footer -->
<footer class="bg-background-dark border-t border-white/5 py-16">
<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
<div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-16">
<div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-2">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-2xl">diamond</span>
<span class="text-lg font-extrabold tracking-[0.2em] text-white uppercase">Luxo DR</span>
</div>
<p class="text-slate-500 text-sm font-light max-w-sm leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Líderes en alquiler de vehículos de alta gama en el Caribe. Ofrecemos exclusividad, potencia y un servicio de concierge diseñado para el estilo de vida más exigente.
                    </p>
<div class="flex gap-4">
<a class="w-10 h-10 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">public</span>
</a>
<a class="w-10 h-10 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">podcasts</span>
</a>
<a class="w-10 h-10 border border-white/10 flex items-center justify-center hover:border-primary text-slate-400 hover:text-primary transition-all" href="#">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-lg">camera</span>
</a>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<h5 class="text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Servicios</h5>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Alquiler VIP</a></li>
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Chófer Privado</a></li>
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Traslados de Lujo</a></li>
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Seguro Premium</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
<div>
<h5 class="text-white text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] mb-6">Legal</h5>
<ul class="space-y-4">
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Privacidad</a></li>
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Términos</a></li>
<li><a class="text-slate-500 text-xs hover:text-primary uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors" href="#">Cookies</a></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<div class="pt-8 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
<p class="text-slate-600 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">© 2024 LUXO DR. Todos los derechos reservados.</p>
<div class="flex gap-6">
<img class="h-4 opacity-30" data-alt="Visa Card Logo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDNJgADCkPHysZ2QjmiiJgMRLxg5Of9ZnrbCLJcIldJCugygeaQg66DCp9ETT9UGbIpiDSEgAUNN8vApdz4Qff_x8I_20oek27QCkGyUB7_7p2K70zOu1IEHN6nz13ChUfRtDqcJ1MgsXaFAePT_XmaJlOCX8pZ4Ve0BfR8PVuMz5nO0BpDcEfwcUgkUKekLEBNTmmwbaQ8GSbvQgzMDTcrdn8-sSjYuIWvIskJ1JKb6G6-SGZv_K6lS6F3CMg_Zmvos3DAPma0jhAE"/>
<img class="h-4 opacity-30" data-alt="Mastercard Logo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCO9cXzn7mQRgTIDftFT02dKu4ceSL7SAAJTLeiuhwDijpJLbc2Z_Gjydyw3RZyiLAIdUT3F_eLgohBGPWj1clzFVnWDt3rAjx0T3OKhYFh414sob7dR-tvefCJAo8Yfsqn9-uvbgt8i0iriQNQm9Nv2pxzBSOgmR8Lp8ycJ-EMudM-D6EeoYMsMGNI9oxXhFw7tnuu6hiyVXSwgGFJZbepb8uwL6QOjuezt-MFIKSbXU9x1bWqGZ9S4wVFC0IzR3n8XH15tLGzvDwj"/>
<img class="h-4 opacity-30" data-alt="American Express Logo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBJckdwg77wrMWlkQTLh1vWjzCEbzHGSkFkuFyeKJlp1hlJ2x2s-JLBut0oZBbJfrx2YIOc3pdZkZYBraHGD1-opJH2dJo7HyoWnzNVBX6jR6WoFDhzVITdvPiwy4RzWyYPkbToRs_z_pPVx0OGxFdYRztjPreg221VHdgyj_SObcjqP1ma2T8oBmIS_FDMkc9NAyAOLr_8HHt0YamkEUpXM9IRpxAhR0ZJEWKqJnhMoGodW79_J4cOtv8NOdOCILLQyQjbKyhkWdIX"/>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</footer>
</Layout>
